### Infinite Tavern API Examples
### Use with REST Client extension in VS Code

@baseUrl = http://localhost:5000/api/game
@gameSessionId = replace-with-actual-game-session-id

###
# Health Check
GET {{baseUrl}}/health

###
# Create New Game
POST {{baseUrl}}/new-game
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "playerName": "Alice",
  "characterName": "Thorin Ironforge",
  "race": "Dwarf",
  "class": "Warrior"
}

###
# Example: Create Elf Mage
POST {{baseUrl}}/new-game
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "playerName": "Bob",
  "characterName": "Elara Moonwhisper",
  "race": "Elf",
  "class": "Mage"
}

###
# Process Turn - Introduce yourself
POST {{baseUrl}}/turn
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "gameSessionId": "{{gameSessionId}}",
  "playerAction": "I approach the tavern keeper and introduce myself"
}

